snippet.title: Marmoreal Trailer
snippet.description:
Marmoreal is a Bullet Hell Action RPG with magical girls, swords and fully automatic crossbows. 


Check out the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1484940/Marmoreal/

Try the Demo on Itch.io: https://zeredek.itch.io/marmoreal

Follow the development on Twitter: https://twitter.com/marmorealdev

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/SMNVwYt7B2

Support me on Patreon if you want: https://www.patreon.com/marmoreal
